title: Son of a Boy Dad: Ep. 49 - Telluride Style
description:
Son of a Boy Dad: Ep. 49 - Telluride Style -- Sas & Rone enjoy some smelling salts, discuss their weekends in Colorado and Florida, hiking, drinking, sex trafficking, Pete Davidson vs. Kanye West, & much, much more -- Full episodes also available on YouTube -- Thanks for listening/watching!
